 see the death of my child. sometimes we find ourselves in similar situations. The burdens of life become so heavy that we think we cannot bear them. David found himself in hopeless situation and he wanted to fly away. Psalm 55 v 1-8</p><p data-block-key=\\\"f5o1g\\\">Even when the burdens of life exceeds our ability to bear them, they never exceeds God&#x27;s ability. 2 Corinthians 1 v 9-10. Hagar should not have been worried, she had the promise of God that he was going to make Ishmael the father of a great nation. Gen 16 v 10-11. Sometimes life hurts so much that we forget the promises of God in our lives. What we fail to see is that our pain is the path God uses to fulfill the promises He has made to us.   </p><p data-block-key=\\\"538lv\\\">the truth is the problems are going to come into our lives, and they will come unannounced and they will hurt us badly. so when they come, we must run to the Lord. He will hear us and He will help us. In verse 16, Hagar sat down and wept. we may ask ourselves why she didn&#x27;t pray                                                     </p>\", \"wagtail_admin_comments\": [], \"gallery_images\": [{\"pk\": 7, \"sort_order\": 0, \"page\": 11, \"image\": \"photos/christsheep.jpg\", \"caption\": \"\"}]}',NULL,11,2),(39,0,'2021-12-02 19:04:06.346909','{\"pk\": 11, \"path\": \"0001000100010005\", \"depth\": 4, \"numchild\": 0, \"translation_key\": \"837b18ab-f41b-4221-9b4e-d90e58522469\", \"locale\": 1, \"title\": \"God has a plan for your life\", \"draft_title\": \"God has a plan for your life\", \"slug\": \"god-has-a-plan-for-your-life\", \"content_type\": 44, \"live\": false, \"has_unpublished_changes\": true, \"url_path\": \"/faith-daily-walk-with-god/devotionals/god-has-a-plan-for-your-life/\", \"owner\": 2, \"seo_title\": \"\", \"show_in_menus\": false, \"search_description\": \"\", \"go_live_at\": null, \"expire_at\": null, \"expired\": false, \"locked\": false, \"locked_at\": null, \"locked_by\": null, \"first_published_at\"