dly. so when they come, we must run to the Lord. He will hear us and He will help us. In verse 16, Hagar sat down and wept. we may ask ourselves why she didn&#x27;t pray. why cry instead of praying. Hagar didn&#x27;t know, but God had been there the whole time. He called her by her name. He won&#x27;t leave you either. You will never live one second of your life or take one step as a child of God without Him. Hebrews 13 v 5.</p><p data-block-key=\\\"192mv\\\">God opened her eyes and showed her what had been therein front of her all along. She saw a well. our problems blind us to His provisions. </p>\", \"wagtail_admin_comments\": [], \"gallery_images\": [{\"pk\": 7, \"sort_order\": 0, \"page\": 11, \"image\": \"photos/christsheep.jpg\", \"caption\": \"\"}]}',NULL,11,2),(40,0,'2021-12-02 22:27:31.398419','{\"pk\": 11, \"path\": \"0001000100010005\", \"depth\": 4, \"numchild\": 0, \"translation_key\": \"837b18ab-f41b-4221-9b4e-d90e58522469\", \"locale\": 1, \"title\": \"God has a plan for your life\", \"draft_title\": \"God has a plan for your life\", \"slug\": \"god-has-a-plan-for-your-life\", \"content_type\": 44, \"live\": false, \"has_unpublished_changes\": true, \"url_path\": \"/faith-daily-walk-with-god/devotionals/god-has-a-plan-for-your-life/\", \"owner\": 2, \"seo_title\": \"\", \"show_in_menus\": false, \"search_description\": \"\", \"go_live_at\": null, \"expire_at\": null, \"expired\": false, \"locked\": false, \"locked_at\": null, \"locked_by\": null, \"first_published_at\": null, \"last_published_at\": null, \"latest_revision_created_at\": \"2021-12-02T19:04:06.346Z\", \"live_revision\": null, \"alias_of\": null, \"date\": \"2021-12-02\", \"verse\": \"<p data-block-key=\\\"esv9m\\\">Genesis 21 v 9- 19</p>\", \"body\": \"<p data-block-key=\\\"496xs\\\">Hagar faces a terrible time of rejection. Sarah became jealous of Ishmael, the son of Hagar the bond woman. She asked Abraham to send Hagar and her son away. saying that Ishmael was not going to have a shar